Class PacketDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.PacketDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Consumer<Packet>

    public final class PacketDispatcher
extends Object
implements Consumer<Packet>
    A Consumer that dispatches the Packet to the right service. So operations are send to the OperationService, events are send to the EventService etc.
